3 Fine-mapping

Columns in tables of fine-mapping results (presented below for each locus):

  • zscore: Z-score of single-SNP association test;
  • pval: the p-value of single-SNP association test;
  • snp_prob: the posterior probability of SNP to be causal (estimated by FINEMAP in the region);
  • snp_log10bf: the associated Bayes Factor (log 10 base);
  • prop_zscore: the ratio between zscore and the best zscore;
  • prop_snp_prob: the ratio between snp_prob and the best snp_prob.
